#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.135"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.135:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.135:0.2"
msgid "13. Avijjāvagga"
msgstr "13. Ignorance"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 135. Tatiyakoṭṭhikasutta → tatiyakoṭṭhitasuttaṃ (bj) | koṭṭhita 3 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.135:0.3"
msgid "135. Tatiyakoṭṭhikasutta"
msgstr "135. Koṭṭhita (3rd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.135:1.1"
msgid "Taññeva nidānaṃ."
msgstr "The same setting."

msgctxt "sn22.135:1.2"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto āyasmantaṃ mahākoṭṭhikaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Sāriputta said to Mahākoṭṭhita:"

msgctxt "sn22.135:1.3"
msgid "“‘avijjā, avijjā’ti, āvuso koṭṭhika, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend Koṭṭhita, they speak of this thing called ‘ignorance’."

msgctxt "sn22.135:1.4"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, āvuso, avijjā;"
msgstr "What is ignorance?"

msgctxt "sn22.135:1.5"
msgid "kittāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti?"
msgstr "And how is an ignorant person defined?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.135:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāvuso, assutavā puthujjano rūpaṃ nappajānāti, rūpasamudayaṃ nappajānāti, "
"rūpanirodhaṃ nappajānāti, rūpanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, it’s when an uneducated ordinary person doesn’t understand form, "
"its origin, its cessation, and the practice that leads to its cessation."

msgctxt "sn22.135:2.2"
msgid "Vedanaṃ nappajānāti … pe …"
msgstr "They don’t understand feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.135:2.3"
msgid "saññaṃ …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.135:2.4"
msgid "saṅkhāre …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.135:2.5"
msgid ""
"viññāṇaṃ nappajānāti, viññāṇasamudayaṃ nappajānāti, viññāṇanirodhaṃ "
"nappajānāti, viññāṇanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr ""
"consciousness, its origin, its cessation, and the practice that leads to its "
"cessation."

msgctxt "sn22.135:2.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccatāvuso, avijjā;"
msgstr "This is called ignorance."

msgctxt "sn22.135:2.7"
msgid "ettāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti."
msgstr "And this is how an ignorant person is defined.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.135:3.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā sāriputto āyasmantaṃ mahākoṭṭhikaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, Venerable Sāriputta said to him:"

msgctxt "sn22.135:3.2"
msgid "“‘vijjā, vijjā’ti, āvuso koṭṭhika, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend Koṭṭhita, they speak of this thing called ‘knowledge’."

msgctxt "sn22.135:3.3"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, āvuso, vijjā;"
msgstr "What is knowledge?"

msgctxt "sn22.135:3.4"
msgid "kittāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti?"
msgstr "And how is a knowledgeable person defined?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli3.177"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.135:4.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāvuso, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpaṃ pajānāti, rūpasamudayaṃ pajānāti, "
"rūpanirodhaṃ pajānāti, rūpanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, it’s when an educated noble disciple understands form, its "
"origin, its cessation, and the practice that leads to its cessation."

msgctxt "sn22.135:4.2"
msgid "Vedanaṃ …"
msgstr "They understand feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.135:4.3"
msgid "saññaṃ …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.135:4.4"
msgid "saṅkhāre …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.135:4.5"
msgid ""
"viññāṇaṃ pajānāti, viññāṇasamudayaṃ pajānāti, viññāṇanirodhaṃ pajānāti, "
"viññāṇanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"consciousness, its origin, its cessation, and the practice that leads to its "
"cessation."

msgctxt "sn22.135:4.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccatāvuso, vijjā;"
msgstr "This is called knowledge."

msgctxt "sn22.135:4.7"
msgid "ettāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti."
msgstr "And this is how a knowledgeable person is defined.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.135:4.8"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.135:4.9"
msgid "Avijjāvaggo tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.135:5.1"
msgid "Samudayadhamme tīṇi,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.135:5.2"
msgid "assādo apare duve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.135:5.3"
msgid "Samudaye ca dve vuttā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.135:5.4"
msgid "koṭṭhike apare tayoti."
msgstr ""
